asset.hookText: Hi TD. We saw your review on Hoover.com. Thanks for taking the time to share your thoughts. What you described isn't typical. We had a few thoughts on what could be wrong, and we put together a video for you. Let us know if you need more help. We want to make sure you love your new Dual Power. -Felicia
